column1: Search query: (("Hantaan virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Dobrova virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Seoul virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Saaremaa virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Amur virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Puumala virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Sin Nombre virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Monongahela virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "New York virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Black Creek Canal virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Bayou virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Choclo virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Andes virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Bermejo virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Lechiguanas virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Maciel virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Oran virus"[Title/Abstract] OR "Laguna Negra virus"[Title/Abstract]) OR ("Haemorrhagic fever with renal syndrome"[Title/Abstract] OR "Hantavirus pulmonary syndrome"[Title/Abstract])) AND (Rodent*[Title/Abstract])
